spec: socket_extra129
version: ">=3.9"
backend: python_module(socket)

docs: https://docs.python.org/3/library/socket.html

provenance:
  derived_from:
    - "https://docs.python.org/3/library/socket.html — Python socket module documentation"
    - "Test vectors verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11"
  not_derived_from:
    - "CPython source: Lib/socket.py"
    - "CPython source: Modules/socketmodule.c"
    - "socket_extra99.zspec.zsdl — covers socket module function __qualname__.__len__() values / SocketIO class identity (ABCMeta, module, bases, qualname length) (table + invariants)."
    - "socket_extra98.zspec.zsdl — covers socket.socket C-level and Python-level method __qualname__.__len__() values (table + invariants)."
    - "socket_extra97.zspec.zsdl — covers socket.socket.__init__/accept/makefile/close __class__.__name__=='function' and __module__=='socket' / socket.socket.send/sendall/fileno __qualname__.__eq__ (table + invariants)."
    - "socket_extra96.zspec.zsdl — covers socket.AF_INET/AF_UNIX/AF_INET6/AF_UNSPEC class names / SOCK_STREAM/SOCK_DGRAM/SOCK_RAW class names / AddressFamily/SocketKind __bases__ / gethostname/gethostbyname/setdefaulttimeout/getdefaulttimeout builtin / getaddrinfo/create_connection Python function (table + invariants)."
    - "socket_extra95.zspec.zsdl — covers AddressFamily/SocketKind enum member values and names / socket.__all__ class name and length (table + invariants)."
    - "socket_extra94.zspec.zsdl — covers socket module-level function __qualname__ and __module__ values (table + invariants)."
    - "socket_extra93.zspec.zsdl — covers socket.socket C-level method_descriptor class names (table + invariants)."
    - "socket.zspec / early extras — cover socket.__name__/__package__ (base spec)."
  notes:
    - "This spec does NOT duplicate invariants present in prior socket spec files."
    - "Wave 274 theme: socket.__all__ list membership — socket/AF_INET/AF_INET6/SOCK_STREAM/SOCK_DGRAM/gethostname/getaddrinfo/create_connection/error/timeout/getfqdn/create_server/IPPROTO_TCP presence / socket.socket.connect/__objclass__.__name__ and __module__ for core method_descriptors."
    - "socket.__all__ is a list with 238 entries. extra95 anchors class name ('list') and length (238)."
    - "'socket' in socket.__all__ == True. Verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0."
    - "'AF_INET' in socket.__all__ == True. Verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0."
    - "'AF_INET6' in socket.__all__ == True. Verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0."
    - "'SOCK_STREAM' in socket.__all__ == True. Verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0."
    - "'SOCK_DGRAM' in socket.__all__ == True. Verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0."
    - "'gethostname' in socket.__all__ == True. Verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0."
    - "'getaddrinfo' in socket.__all__ == True. Verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0."
    - "'create_connection' in socket.__all__ == True. Verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0."
    - "'error' in socket.__all__ == True. Verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0."
    - "'timeout' in socket.__all__ == True. Verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0."
    - "'getfqdn' in socket.__all__ == True. Verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0."
    - "'create_server' in socket.__all__ == True. Verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0."
    - "'IPPROTO_TCP' in socket.__all__ == True. Verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0."
    - "socket.socket.connect.__objclass__.__name__ == 'socket'. Verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0."
    - "socket.socket.bind.__objclass__.__name__ == 'socket'. Verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0."
    - "socket.socket.listen.__objclass__.__name__ == 'socket'. Verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0."
    - "socket.socket.recv.__objclass__.__name__ == 'socket'. Verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0."
    - "socket.socket.send.__objclass__.__name__ == 'socket'. Verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0."
    - "socket.socket.setsockopt.__objclass__.__name__ == 'socket'. Verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0."
    - "socket.socket.connect.__objclass__.__module__ == '_socket'. Verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0."
    - "socket.socket.recv.__objclass__.__module__ == '_socket'. Verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0."
    - "Note: extra95 first anchors socket.__all__ class name ('list') and length (238); this spec anchors __all__ membership for specific named entries."
    - "Note: socket.socket.connect/bind/listen/recv/send/setsockopt are C-level method_descriptors from socketmodule.c. Their __objclass__ is the socket class from the _socket extension module (__module__=='_socket')."
    - "Note: 'SocketIO' is NOT in socket.__all__ (verified). 'setblocking' is NOT in socket.__all__. The 238-entry list includes address family constants, protocol constants, and Python-level functions."
    - "All expected values verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
  created_at: "2026-04-11T00:00:00Z"

